Source: kazoo
Section: python
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Neil Williams <neil@reddit.com>
Build-Depends: python-setuptools (>= 0.6b3),
               python-all (>= 2.6.6-3),
               debhelper (>= 8.0.0)
